  <entry>
    <title>java面向对象方面知识点(一)</title>
    <url>/2020/06/23/JAVA%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="java面向对象方面知识点-一"><a href="#java面向对象方面知识点-一" class="headerlink" title="java面向对象方面知识点(一)"></a>java面向对象方面知识点(一)</h1><p>此博客旨在总结Java在面向对象方面的知识点，包含Java编程的进阶知识。</p>
<h3 id="super关键字"><a href="#super关键字" class="headerlink" title="super关键字"></a>super关键字</h3><p>在继承中，父类可以调用子类的方法，但相反的情况下就会被限制。但我们可以利用super这个关键字来实现(super只发生在子类中)。</p>
<p>例如：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;父类</span><br><span class="line">public class Animal &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    private String name;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    private int age;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public void eat()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       System.out.println(&quot;动物要饿肚子啦&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public String getName() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return name;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public void setName(String name) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        this.name &#x3D; name;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public int getAge() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return age;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;子类</span><br><span class="line">public class Dog extends Animal&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public void eat()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; 调用父类的方法</span><br><span class="line">        super.eat();</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;狗狗喜欢吃肉骨头&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>当父类只有一个有参数的构造函数的时候，子类也必须要含有这个构造函数，可使用super关键字来实现。</p>
<p>例如：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class JavaFile extends CustomFile&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F; 声明一个构造函数</span><br><span class="line">  public JavaFile(String filePath)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F;调用父类的构造函数</span><br><span class="line">    super(filePath);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>如果需要定义新的构造函数，则：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class JavaFile extends CustomFile&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  private String packageName;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F; 声明一个构造函数</span><br><span class="line">  public JavaFile(String filePath,String packageName)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    super(filePath);</span><br><span class="line">    this.packageName &#x3D; packageName;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  public String getPackageName()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      return this.packageName;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>注意：构造函数中的super方法需要写在第一行!</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JAVA</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>JAVA</tag>
      </tags>
